\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec3 Establishing source control using Git\
\ls2\ilvl0\cf2 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\cf2 \expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec3 Creating a repeatable build and release process\
\ls2\ilvl0\cf2 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\cf2 \expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec3 Introducing continuous integration\
